posts.post_content: Any grade is fine. PM me if you have one laying around !!

I specifically collect Murph since he is a relative. I was able to get one but it's in my murphy collection. Someone else had offered me one not long ago. Let me check my emails and see if it's still available. 

Ron
Ron, Thanks for offering to help locate one. I appreciate the effort !!
